Interface DirectoryService

    public interface DirectoryService

      • findAgreements

        List<Agreement> findAgreements(String orgNumber,
                             String productId)
        Finds all agreements with the given productId for the given actor.
        Parameters:
        orgNumber - the actor of the agreement.
        productId - the id of the product.
        Returns:
        A list of all agreements that match the given actor and productId. If no agreement is found an empty list is returned.
